---
// Страница "О компании" в тёмной теме
// Стиль: "Тёплый огонь" — как v4 главной
// Все тексты сохранены с оригинала
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>О компании — С лёгким паром</title>
    <meta name="description" content="С 2014 года создаём бани, которые служат долгие годы. Производство в Пестово, Новгородская область. Доставка по всей России.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0D0D0D;
            --bg-medium: #151515;
            --bg-light: #1A1A1A;
            --text: #FAFAFA;
            --text-secondary: #A8A8A8;
            --text-muted: #707070;
            --accent: #D4915E;
            --accent-hover: #E5A36E;
            --border: #2A2A2A;
        }

        html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .serif { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 400; }
        a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
        img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(13,13,13,0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .header-inner {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .header-nav {
            display: none;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .header-nav a {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .header-nav a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

        .header-phone {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: var(--text);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .header-phone::before {
            content: '';
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            padding: 10rem 1.5rem 6rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .hero-inner {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Stats Bento */
        .stats {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
        }

        .stats-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1px;
            background: var(--border);
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--bg-medium);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-card--wide {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--accent);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .stat-desc {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Founder */
        .founder {
            display: grid;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .founder-photo {
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .founder-photo img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .founder-content {
            padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .founder-inner {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .founder-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .founder-name {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .founder-text p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        .founder-text strong {
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .founder-signature {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Timeline */
        .timeline {
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
        }

        .timeline-inner {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .timeline h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .timeline-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1px;
            background: var(--border);
        }

        .timeline-card {
            background: var(--bg-medium);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .timeline-year {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            line-height: 1;
            min-width: 100px;
        }

        .timeline-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Team */
        .team {
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .team-inner {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .team h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .team-card {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .team-photo {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .team-photo img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .team-name {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .team-role {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .team-phone {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .team-phone:hover {
            color: var(--accent-hover);
        }

        /* Production */
        .production {
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
        }

        .production-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .production-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .production h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .production-text {
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .production-gallery {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .production-item {
            aspect-ratio: 16/9;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .production-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.85;
            transition: all 0.5s;
        }

        .production-item:hover img {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }

        /* Safety */
        .safety {
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .safety-inner {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .safety h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .safety-text {
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .safety h3 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .safety-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .safety-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .safety-list li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0.7rem;
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .safety-certificate {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .safety-certificate img {
            max-width: 300px;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .safety-certificate img:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .zoom-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .zoom-btn:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Contacts */
        .contacts {
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
        }

        .contacts-inner {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contacts h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .contacts-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .contacts-card {
            padding: 2rem;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .contacts-card h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .contacts-phone {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .contacts-phone:hover {
            color: var(--accent-hover);
        }

        .contacts-hint {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .contacts-address {
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .contacts-social {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .contacts-social a {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .contacts-social a:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .req-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .req-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.25rem;
        }

        .req-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .req-value {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        /* Lightbox */
        .lightbox {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .lightbox--open {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }

        .lightbox__overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95);
        }

        .lightbox__content {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 90%;
            max-height: 90%;
        }

        .lightbox__image {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 90vh;
        }

        .lightbox__close {
            position: absolute;
            top: -3rem;
            right: 0;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Modal */
        .modal {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .modal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }

        .modal__overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
        }

        .modal__container {
            position: relative;
            background: var(--bg-medium);
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 90%;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .modal__close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1rem;
            right: 1rem;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .modal__close:hover {
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .modal__title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .modal__text {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .modal__field {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .modal__field input,
        .modal__field textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text);
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .modal__field input:focus,
        .modal__field textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .modal__field textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 100px;
        }

        .modal__submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .modal__submit:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
        }

        .modal__privacy {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .modal__privacy a {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .modal__success {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .modal__success-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .modal__success-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .modal__success-text {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .team-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .production-gallery { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .contacts-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .header { padding: 1.5rem 3rem; }
            .header-nav { display: flex; }
            .founder { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .founder-content { padding: 4rem 3rem; }
            .safety-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
            .stats-grid .stat-card--wide { grid-column: 1; }
            .production-gallery { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
            .req-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-inner">
            <a href="/test/v4" class="logo">С ЛЁГКИМ ПАРОМ</a>
            <nav class="header-nav">
                <a href="/test/v4#collection">Проекты</a>
                <a href="/test/v4#craft">Доставка</a>
                <a href="/test/about">О компании</a>
                <a href="/test/v4#contact">Контакты</a>
            </nav>
            <a href="tel:88003500393" class="header-phone">8-800-350-03-93</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-inner">
            <h1>С 2014 года создаём бани, которые служат долгие годы</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Производство в Пестово, Новгородская область. Доставка по всей России.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
        <div class="stats-inner">
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card stat-card--wide">
                    <div class="stat-number">800K</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">километров доставки</div>
                    <p class="stat-desc">Столько проехали наши бани — из Пестово в 18 регионов страны</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">10</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">лет на рынке</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">30+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">бань в месяц</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">538</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">единиц техники</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">видео на YouTube</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="founder">
        <div class="founder-photo">
            <img src="/images/about/founder.webp" alt="Георгий Дзамуков — основатель компании С лёгким паром" loading="eager" width="640" height="480">
        </div>
        <div class="founder-content">
            <div class="founder-inner">
                <div class="founder-label">Основатель</div>
                <h2 class="founder-name">Георгий Дзамуков</h2>
                <div class="founder-text">
                    <p>Привет! Меня зовут Георгий, и я основал «С лёгким паром» в 2014 году.</p>
